i965G[M] cannot relocate objects above 4GiB.
Ensure ttm uses dma32 on these systems.

Signed-off-by: Robert Beckett <bob.beckett@collabora.com>
Reviewed-by: Thomas Hellstr√∂m <thomas.hellstrom@linux.intel.com>
